<h2 id="ncts4">NCTS4</h2>

<h3 id="ncts4-what-we-re-working-on-now">What we’re working on now</h3>

<p>CTC Guarantee Balance API v1.0 is feature complete and we do not currently plan to make any changes to the API.</p>
<h3 id="ncts4-updates">Updates</h3>

<p>CTC Guarantee Balance API v1.0 will be withdrawn soon after the UK NCTS5 service goes live. We will tell you the exact date nearer the time.</p>
